<L>__{exterior stud farm day}
<A>__{roderick buying a horse.}
<C>__{roderick }
<D>__{in the midst of my difficulties, i promised to buy a little horse for my dear little patrick, which was to be a present for his eighth birthday, that was now coming on. i may have had my faults, but no man shall dare to say of me that i was not a good and tender father.}
<A>__{roderick admires the horse.}
<C>__{roderick }
<D>__{it was a beautiful little animal, and stood me in a good sum. i never regarded money for that dear child.}
